Version of minikube:
minikube version

minikube start ---> start the cluster of single node.

kubectl --> is the client to communicate to api server.

Kubectl commands:

kubectl version
kubectl cluster-info
kubectl get nodes or kubectl get no
kubectl get namespace or kubectl get ns
---Create Namespace-----
kubectl create namespace itrain-jaquar
--------------------------------------
kubectl get deployments
kubectl get pods
kubectl get services

---------Kubernetes configuration------

kubectl config vew
kubectl config set-context itrain-jaquar --cluster=minikube --user=minikube --namespace=itrain-jaquar
kubectl config use-context itrain-jaquar
kubectl config current-context

---Deployments-----
kubectl create -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/itrainpadman/k8s_resouces/master/nginx-deployment.yaml
kubectl delete -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/itrainpadman/k8s_resouces/master/nginx-deployment.yaml

